name: Beauty Girl Dress Up
description:
Play a fashion dress up game, make you to become a beautiful girl.
This is a fashion game of dress up. Dress up to be a beautiful girl.
Dream to be a beautiful girl, this is a good guide for you to learn. It's as easy as ever to create the perfect look with Dress up - Beauty girl.

- 4 model to choose
- Many decorate to add
- Save and share to your friends
